    "description": "AIIMS Delhi Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Radiologist for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout AIIMS Delhi Ventures Solutions:\nAIIMS Delhi Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AIIMS Delhi Ventures Solutions!",
